            <p>
              Choose <c>8:</c><m>\chi^2</m><c>cdf</c>.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>
              Enter the lower bound, which is generally the chi-square value.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>
              Enter the upper bound.
              Use a large number, such as 1000.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>
              Enter the degrees of freedom.
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p>
